  <div class="legend-item"><div class="leg-box leg-fk"></div><span>Foreign Key (FK)</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="leg-box leg-col"></div><span>Attribute</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item" style="color:#34d399">── 1:N relationship</div>
  <div class="legend-item" style="color:#f472b6">╌╌ M:N (via junction)</div>
